      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so you're saying abstract b's approach is basically less \"scientific\" because it doesn't use quantitative metrics? do you think a study using those indigenous frameworks could ever actually meet the standards of a top-tier journal, or are they inherently less valid in a professional academic setting?",
